{
  "name": "Emphatic Expert",
  "type": "feat",
  "img": "icons/magic/symbols/runes-star-magenta.webp",
  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Category: Genjutsu </p><p>Prerequisite: Level 8+ </p><p>You can feel every thought. Every intent. Every passing idea.</p><p> When casting a Genjutsu that does not deal damage, you gain the following benefits: </p><p>• Increase your Wisdom score by 1, to a maximum of 20.</p><p>• When you would cast a Genjutsu that targets a single creature, on a failed save, that creatures' movement speed is reduced by 20 feet for the duration.</p><p>• When you would cast a Genjutsu that can affect two or more creatures at once, on a failed save, once per turn, all affected creatures take psychic damage whenever one of the other affected creatures take damage of any type, excluding the creature that triggers this effect.</p><p> The number of psychic damage creatures take is an amount equal to the rank of the jutsu currently affecting them all.</p><p> (D-Rank: 2d4, C-Rank: 4d4, B-Rank: 6d4, A-Rank: 8d4, S-Rank: 10d4)</p>",
